title: SHILL: you realize the intellectual caliber of the critics I'm facing. :-/
description:
The video being criticized here is an old one: "The Death of a Dream: Veganism After the End of HCLF / RT4 / Durianrider / Freelee /etc."
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tgJMKXJadlE
This might be an appropriate time to mention my thematically-related video (i.e., salient to this criticism), ""Chase Your Dreams" = BAD ADVICE NOBODY WANTS TO HEAR."
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fwBUTFdNe14
My critic (who believes that you can cure Crohn's disease and schizophrenia through "fruit and fasting") can be found here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgXcU3g82RNg56ijEZE-Ekg/videos

Incidentally, I notice that he did (many months ago) make a short (two minute) video simply stating that Durianrider was in the wrong, and that I was in the right: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1z5WFoa7dJs
